      "text": "いっつもお茶ばっかり。今日こそ練習しますよ",
      "startTime": 48.1117203953,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "konyui",
      "speakerName": "平沢唯",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-konyui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "かたいこと言わないでよあずにゃん～",
      "startTime": 52.7994754396,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "konyui",
      "speakerName": "平沢唯",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-konyui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2305_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2305_01_02-konyui003.wav",
      "text": "それで、どうしたの？",
      "startTime": 55.8666635513,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "みなさんの曲は、私達が普段歌うアイドルソングとは",
      "startTime": 57.9766862633,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2305_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2305_01_02-suz003.wav",
      "text": "また違う世界観だな、と感じましたの",
      "startTime": 62.3614191375,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "だから、普段みなさんがどうやって曲を作っているか",
      "startTime": 66.3680920682,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2305_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2305_01_02-suz004.wav",
      "text": "どんな活動をしているのかを聞かせてくださらない？",
      "startTime": 70.5666635513,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "konyui",
      "speakerName": "平沢唯",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-konyui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "う～ん、私達の活動か～",
